## Courses

<div class="courses-container"><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BIOS 7060</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Applied Machine Learning for Healthcare</h3><p class="course-description">Learn to apply machine learning techniques to healthcare data, including supervised and unsupervised learning, deep learning, and model validation in clinical settings.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/applied-ml-healthcare" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/applied-ml-healthcare/tree/main/slides" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/applied-ml-healthcare" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BIOS 6050</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Foundations of Health Data Science</h3><p class="course-description">Master fundamental concepts in health data science including data management, statistical analysis, visualization, and reproducible research practices.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/health-data-science" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/health-data-science/tree/main/lectures" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/health-data-science" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 7020</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Bioinformatics Bootcamp</h3><p class="course-description">Intensive hands-on training in bioinformatics tools and techniques, covering sequence analysis, genomics, and computational biology workflows.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/bioinformatics-bootcamp" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/bioinformatics-bootcamp/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/bioinformatics-bootcamp" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">STAT 5530</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Data Analysis with R</h3><p class="course-description">Comprehensive introduction to data analysis using R, covering data manipulation, statistical modeling, and visualization for research applications.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/data-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/data-analysis-r/tree/main/slides" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/data-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 6010</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">R for Bioinformatics</h3><p class="course-description">Learn to use R for bioinformatics applications including sequence analysis, phylogenetics, and biological data visualization.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-bioinformatics" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-bioinformatics/tree/main/lectures" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-bioinformatics" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 7030</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Machine Learning for Bioinformatics</h3><p class="course-description">Apply machine learning methods to biological problems including protein structure prediction, gene expression analysis, and drug discovery.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/ml-bioinformatics" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/ml-bioinformatics/tree/main/slides" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/ml-bioinformatics" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BIOS 5040</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Python for Health Data Analysis</h3><p class="course-description">Master Python programming for health data analysis including pandas, numpy, scikit-learn, and healthcare-specific libraries.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/python-health-data" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/python-health-data/tree/main/lectures" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/python-health-data" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">GIS 6020</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Python for Geospatial Health Data Science</h3><p class="course-description">Learn to analyze geospatial health data using Python, including mapping disease patterns, spatial statistics, and environmental health applications.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/geospatial-health-python" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/geospatial-health-python/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/geospatial-health-python" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 8010</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">RNA-seq Data Analysis with R</h3><p class="course-description">Comprehensive workflow for RNA-seq analysis including quality control, differential expression, pathway analysis, and visualization.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/rnaseq-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/rnaseq-analysis-r/tree/main/slides" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/rnaseq-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 8020</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Single-cell RNA-seq Analysis with R</h3><p class="course-description">Advanced techniques for single-cell RNA-seq analysis including clustering, trajectory analysis, and cell type identification.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/scrnaseq-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/scrnaseq-analysis-r/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/scrnaseq-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BIOS 6070</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">Building Dashboards with R</h3><p class="course-description">Create interactive dashboards and web applications using R Shiny, plotly, and other visualization tools for health data.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-dashboards" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-dashboards/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-dashboards" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">BINF 8030</span><span class="course-type workshop">Workshop</span></div><h3 class="course-title">TCGA Data Analysis with R</h3><p class="course-description">Access and analyze cancer genomics data from The Cancer Genome Atlas using R and Bioconductor packages.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/tcga-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/tcga-analysis-r/tree/main/slides" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/tcga-analysis-r" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">STAT 5010</span><span class="course-type seminar">Seminar</span></div><h3 class="course-title">gtsummary for Public Health</h3><p class="course-description">Master the gtsummary R package for creating publication-ready summary tables and statistical reports in public health research.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/gtsummary-public-health" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/gtsummary-public-health/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/gtsummary-public-health" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">STAT 4020</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">R for Research</h3><p class="course-description">Comprehensive R programming course focused on research applications, reproducible research, and advanced statistical analysis.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-for-research" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-for-research/tree/main/lectures" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/r-for-research" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div><div class="course-card"><div class="course-header"><span class="course-code">STAT 3010</span><span class="course-type course">Course</span></div><h3 class="course-title">SPSS for Health Sciences</h3><p class="course-description">Learn statistical analysis using SPSS with focus on health sciences applications including descriptive statistics, hypothesis testing, and regression analysis.</p><div class="course-links"><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/spss-health-sciences" target="_blank" class="course-link">Syllabus</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/spss-health-sciences/tree/main/materials" target="_blank" class="course-link">Slides</a><a href="https://github.com/hossainlab/spss-health-sciences" target="_blank" class="course-link">Code</a></div></div></div>

:::

